pageContext.claim: “Well, I think the Kavanaugh hearings have really galvanized the Republican Party. People saw how horribly this number one student at Yale, and when he sat there and said, what I really did is I work so hard of becoming number one in my class, and I could understand that so well, and people understood it. And the Democrats did too.”
pageContext.analysis: Kavanaugh was not the top of his class in college at Yale University. Yale Law School does not rank students.
